OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSunshine and
OL,6,Fblustery showers continuing this
OL,7,Fevening, some of the showers may be
OL,8,Fheavy at times. Drier conditions for a
OL,9,Ftime but showers may return by the
OL,10,Fmorning. A chilly night with
OL,11,Ftemperatures a few degrees cooler in
OL,12,Frural parts.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA cloudy start with perhaps
OL,15,Fone or two showers in the morning.
OL,16,FShowers becoming more widespread and
OL,17,Fpotentially turning heavy and thundery
OL,18,Fin places by the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
