OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FWet
OL,6,Fand windy Thursday morning, turning
OL,7,Fdrier by the evening but remaining
OL,8,Fbreezy. Largely dry Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday with perhaps showers
OL,10,Fdeveloping Friday afternoon.
OL,11,FTemperatures returning to around
OL,12,Faverage.
